# Linux Commands: https://www.mireene.com/webimg/linux_tip1.htm

#### Basic Setting ####
1. Connect Cloud Server
ssh awekim@4.234.234.12

2. Set root account's password
>> sudo passwd 

3. Log in as root account (or super user)
>> su

4. Update apt
>> update apt

5. Install Apache2
>> apt install apache2

6. Install net tools
>> apt install net-tools

7. Check network status
>> netstat -lntp | grep apache2

8. Install Tomcat (data trasfer software, uses port 8080)
>> apt install tomcat9

9. Link Apache & Tomcat
>> apt install libapache2-mod-jk

#### File Access Grant ####
After installing FileZilla, you may face this issue of file grant.
Open Terminal and run following code.
>> chown -R awekim /var/www/

